### modify concert basic
PATCH http://localhost:8080/admin/concerts/4/basic
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "첫번째 콘서트(수정)",
  "detailInfo": "첫번째로 오픈하는 콘서트입니다.(수정)",
  "runningTime": 120,
  "ticketingStartTime": "2025-11-30T18:00",
  "openTime": "2025-11-01T09:00",
  "rounds": [
    {
      "startDateTime": "2025-12-02T18:00"
    }
  ]
}

### modify concert place
PATCH http://localhost:8080/admin/concerts/4/place
Content-Type: application/json

